10. TERMINATION

    Your rights under this license terminate automatically and without
    notice if you breach any of its terms. Upon termination, you must
    immediately cease all use and distribution of the Covered Work and
    destroy any copies in your possession or control. Termination does
    not affect the rights of any third parties who received compliant
